know he'll forgive too.

01:12:45.321 --> 01:12:46.779
I swore an oath.

01:12:46.780 --> 01:12:48.365
- What happens
when Yar kills you?

01:12:50.993 --> 01:12:53.078
- Then it will be bad, Lutobor.

01:12:54.413 --> 01:12:55.747
You'll be sacrificed

01:12:55.748 --> 01:12:57.832
